{"tid":420113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（學術討論）大家訓覺多唔多發夢","createTime":"2017-10-01T06:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T07:41:48.000Z","uid":141573,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f733a1d56eedb863af2bbe5c13349fbcdfa3c47","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"我自己訓覺差唔多次次都發夢 <br />\n而且會記得個夢<br />\n但我身邊有人訓覺係唔會發夢<br />\n但唔知佢真係發過夢唔記得定真係沒發夢<br />\n之前睇過篇文章 <br />\n人真正休息時間得2～3個鐘 係唔會發夢  稱為深層睡眠（好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n有沒人巴打有研究過 點先為之訓得好 <br />\n發夢定唔發夢代表好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 訓覺一定要發夢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔嬲都唔發夢"},{"pid":"2e397ec7bb925e2dfd560fdd07e47235f08eea5c","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"dfdae437f52134af34ce1a0f7052ec0a90444ee6","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:37:29.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"6122decf8b5175ba9fed7c79dcda3efb4eac443f","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"73068543fc5e6957e82229b323a163dc0a741de6","tid":420113,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5fac7665bb8655c0bd9d38757bec13ad96119ecc","tid":420113,"uid":64493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:38:34.000Z","msg":"壓力大既時候 訓晏覺都會發夢"},{"pid":"4d50f1f5fdf8155f25bf11f67497c79dcbbcb196","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:40:43.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"a6bbd127a8db7441bb528515aed2c9db6949a3dc","tid":420113,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"日日都有 好定唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9195189b475d241cb77e44d9dfd31b82cec5b8","tid":420113,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"有時未訓著都會發夢<br />\n叫睡前幻覺"},{"pid":"8905d052b05ad400264607cbe55b0243c8d37383","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壓力大既時候 訓晏覺都會發夢</blockquote><br />\n關壓力事咩原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ecd1c2efe4d73efc906245bbb187b9117c77ae","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"求全能既連登仔解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c982e96be8f1b001e07e4c7aadd1bcb5b07463a","tid":420113,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"有記憶以來得一次無發，真係好舒服<br />\n合埋眼下一秒就開眼，精神回復曬，但有種無左啲時間既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08f877518fe771d55f868b8681458f7ed1ead47","tid":420113,"uid":12984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"日日都發<br />\n記得哂d 夢<br />\n如果無啦啦chok 醒左再訓 個夢會繼續"},{"pid":"18e8ce77084fd98aeda2943a3d7376c326be19a0","tid":420113,"uid":64972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"有時啲夢 現實會出現番個情境 似曾相識"},{"pid":"691737e73ac0e83cb233b4e457dc232ac444d9d0","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日都發<br />\n記得哂d 夢<br />\n如果無啦啦chok 醒左再訓 個夢會繼續</blockquote><br />\n咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時發緊春夢比人嘈醒左就發唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac1a925385735d7c89e4e1747187097b9710841","tid":420113,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"